    <item>
      <title>受美国销售强劲和日元疲软影响，本田利润创历史新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/honda-profit-rises-to-record-high-on-strong-us-sales-weak-yen</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国市场销售强劲，克服了中国市场经济放缓的影响，本田汽车公司第一季度营业利润升至历史新高，使这家日本第二大汽车制造商有望再创利润纪录。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/honda-profit-rises-to-record-high-on-strong-us-sales-weak-yen</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 06:41:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高盛认为中国供应过剩状况将缓解——但不包括电动汽车</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/goldman-sachs-sees-china-oversupply-easing-just-not-for-evs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛分析师表示，未来几年中国海外商品出口趋势将发生改变，但电动汽车和钢铁行业出口放缓的趋势不太可能得到缓解。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/goldman-sachs-sees-china-oversupply-easing-just-not-for-evs</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 06:23:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>嘉能可因股东反对而放弃退出煤炭业务的计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/glencore-abandons-plan-to-exit-coal-after-shareholders-say-no</link>
      <description><![CDATA[嘉能可公司 (Glencore Plc) 宣布将退出煤炭业务，而仅仅九个月前，该公司曾表示将退出利润丰厚但污染严重的煤炭业务，但在与反对该计划的股东进行讨论后，该公司最终放弃了剥离煤炭部门的计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/glencore-abandons-plan-to-exit-coal-after-shareholders-say-no</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 06:05:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着富人交易量增加，新加坡银行的财富费用激增</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/dbs-earnings-beat-estimates-with-gains-in-lending-wealth-fees</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新加坡最大的几家银行因富人向这个亚洲财富中心转移资产和进行交易的兴趣而获益，这提高了这些银行的盈利。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/dbs-earnings-beat-estimates-with-gains-in-lending-wealth-fees</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 04:16:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着收益率进一步下降，中国打击债券泡沫的斗争进一步升级</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/pboc-decides-to-forgo-cash-injections-for-first-time-since-2020</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国央行与国债购买者之间的争斗正在愈演愈烈，尽管越来越多的证据表明官方对此表示不满，但交易商仍在继续抢购国债。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/pboc-decides-to-forgo-cash-injections-for-first-time-since-2020</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 04:13:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本央行言论助推日韩股市上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/asian-stocks-rise-as-boj-comments-helps-lift-japan-korea-shares</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在日本央行表示如果金融市场不稳定则不会加息之后，亚洲股市在周一全球股市暴跌之后连续第二个交易日上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/asian-stocks-rise-as-boj-comments-helps-lift-japan-korea-shares</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 03:22:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本央行行长内田改变利率观点，日元在波动交易中下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/yen-extends-losses-against-dollar-as-market-volatility-continues</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本央行副行长内田新一表示，如果金融市场不稳定，政策制定者将不会提高基准利率，此后，日元周三在震荡交​​易中继续走低。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/yen-extends-losses-against-dollar-as-market-volatility-continues</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 01:49:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
